-- India Examining Tax Implications on Other Mergers After Vodafone
-- B y   T u s h a r   D h a r a
-- 2010-10-26T07:39:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/india-examining-tax-implications-on-other-mergers-after-vodafone-law-suit.html
India is examining tax implications
on other mergers and acquisitions after a case related to
Vodafone Group Plc unit’s purchase of Hutchison Whampoa Ltd.’s
mobile phone unit in the South Asian nation, S.S.N. Moorthy,
chairman of the Central Board of Direct Taxes, said in New Delhi
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
